00:54:06.340 --> 00:54:08.720
that's the very moment
which you should realize

00:54:08.720 --> 00:54:11.793
that you're subject to a very
characteristic human delusion.

00:54:12.916 --> 00:54:16.430
But in that case, again,
we're understanding the state

00:54:18.294 --> 00:54:21.300
that the thing they're
doing that's a deviation

00:54:21.300 --> 00:54:24.215
from what's reasonable, in
terms of what it would be like

00:54:24.215 --> 00:54:26.247
for them to do the reasonable thing

00:54:26.247 --> 00:54:28.940
